      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING ALI (2) is better than last start when fourth (19.78) from Box 2 at this track over 340m. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Has ability and looks hard to stop. LADY CHAOS (7) is worth forgiving last start after finishing eighth (19.21) from Box 6 at Richmond over 320m. Shapes as one to consider. BEAUTIFUL MAGPIE (8) should enjoy clear running from the outside box. Below best latest at Gosford (30.48) when 6th and beaten 12 lengths. Form here at this distance is strong including one wins. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Great chance to atone. TURBO MISS (1) has to be respected despite coming off a five-and-a-half months break.",
